quizzes.question:
Fill in the blanks to output "Hi" using echo:
[!raw!]
<?{0}
   {1} "Hi";
?>

quizzes.textContent:
[h1]PHP Statements[/h1]

Each PHP statement must end with a [b]semicolon[/b].[code format="php" codeId="458"]<?php
  echo "A";
  echo "B";
  echo "C";
?>[/code]
[note]Forgetting to add a semicolon at the end of a statement results in an [b]error[/b].[/note]
